best to ensure the event is safe and secure for everyone; our health and
wellness plan is being developed in partnership with The International Centre
and our other suppliers. </mj-text>
         <mj-text color="#000" font-weight="400" font-size="19px" font-weight="400" align="left">We will also continue to monitor the announcements from Public Health
